# <type>: <description>
#
# Types:
#   feat: new feature
#   fix: bug fix
#   docs: documentation
#   style: formatting, no code change
#   refactor: code restructuring
#   test: adding/modifying tests
#   chore: maintenance tasks
#
# Rules:
#   - Use present tense ("add" not "added")
#   - Use imperative mood ("move" not "moves")
#   - Keep first line under 72 characters
#   - Be specific and factual
#   - Avoid hyperbole or percentages
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add timer event support to simulator
#   fix: handle null values in expression evaluator
#   refactor: extract parser logic into separate module
#   test: add coverage for vector operations
#   docs: update API documentation for chat functions